  "detailed_description": "Play the game... <strong>SEES GAME!!</strong><br>Play as Sees in a reimagined take of the classic Snake game.<br>Eat apples and compete with your friends for the hi-score!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/90c54ebe6d8efd492f8b55a2e45b95b4.avif?t=1742500440\" width=200 height=202 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10 diferent mazes.<br></li><li> 3 game modes, 2 of them unlockable after reaching a certain amount of points:<br><u>Normal:</u> Make your way through the randomly selected labyrinths.<br><u>Classic:</u> No walls! One mistake and it's Game Over. <br><u>Time Trial:</u> Keep eatng apples before the time runs out. Can't pause in this mode.<br></li><li> Unlockable skins.<br></li><li> 8-bit style soundtrack arranged by Marcelo Canario.<br></li><li> Easter eggs!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to play:</strong></h2>Use <strong>arrow keys</strong> or <strong>WASD</strong> to move around.<br><br>Press <strong>Q</strong> or <strong>P</strong> to pause the game (you have a 3 seconds cooldown to pause again).<br><br>Press <strong>C</strong> to switch the camera.<br><br>Eating apples makes you faster. Careful though, because you get REALLY fast.<br><br><strong>Red Apples</strong> give you 1 point. <strong>Golden Apples</strong> give you 2 points.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/5947110c6054da5322104a2088d14330.poster.avif?t=1742500440\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/5947110c6054da5322104a2088d14330.webm?t=1742500440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/5947110c6054da5322104a2088d14330.mp4?t=1742500440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Some mazes feature tunnels you can go through. Play <strong>seestrategically!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/4030b41ca3122db877b747433cdd0be1.poster.avif?t=1742500440\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/4030b41ca3122db877b747433cdd0be1.webm?t=1742500440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/4030b41ca3122db877b747433cdd0be1.mp4?t=1742500440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Credits:</strong></h2><strong>Kovaldevlog:</strong> Basically all the magic.<br><strong>Rodricoro:</strong> Big loser, no one cares.",
