c6054da5322104a2088d14330.mp4?t=1742500440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Some mazes feature tunnels you can go through. Play <strong>seestrategically!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/4030b41ca3122db877b747433cdd0be1.poster.avif?t=1742500440\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/4030b41ca3122db877b747433cdd0be1.webm?t=1742500440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673330/extras/4030b41ca3122db877b747433cdd0be1.mp4?t=1742500440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Credits:</strong></h2><strong>Kovaldevlog:</strong> Basically all the magic.<br><strong>Rodricoro:</strong> Big loser, no one cares.",
